# Agent intent & parallel work

**Board:** `.cursor/agent-intents/BOARD.md` — read before editing shared areas; add/update your entry (`active` → `done`), unique **Agent** handle (not raw model name), narrow **Touching**, heartbeat on same local date = fresh; never remove another agent’s `active` row; stale → `stale-suspect` or remove. Typical fields: Session, Heartbeat, Status, Touching, Avoiding, Notes.

**Overlap:** Unexpected diffs or active board rows → assume parallel work; narrow scope, re-read files, **stage only your files**, ask before ambiguous edits. Never overwrite/commit others’ work without confirmation.

**Push (`origin/master`):** Before `git push`: `git fetch origin` and `git pull` (or `git pull --rebase origin master`). See `docs/plans/avklarat/external-review-execution/CONTINUATION.md` (Principer).
